addInstrRootGuardian.t.sol
├── given sender does not have the relevant role
│  └── it should revert with AccessManagedUnauthorized
└── given sender has the relevant role
   ├── given provided address is already a root guardian
   │  └── it should revert with AlreadyRootGuardian
   └── given provided address is not already a root guardian
      ├── it should set the provided address as a root guardian
      └── it should emit a InstrRootGuardianAdded event
